Hi there !

I'm a beginner indie game developer, and this is the Demo version of my game.

Your thoughts are very important to me. It will be very helpful for future improvements.

If you can make a small donation it would be greatly appreciated.
(Donors names will be displayed on the full version of this game. And it will be published on playstore and other web game sites.(100% free game , anyone can play))

Finally thanks for playing, donating and commenting.

The full version will be coming soon :)  Thanks all !
